metadata.description: Music is love, floating in the air, and flowing like water too, plants have known this long before we came into the picture...that is why they sing and dance this time. Sound Sprouts is a really cool ecosystem where you can build, decor and design your own gardens; share your gardens with your friends, make them playable, make them popular, show them off... unleash your creativity with Sound Sprouts.This NFT Collection has 9,999 unique plants and 90 immersive combinations of music. Eyes and ears fully on at Sound Sprouts.
metadata.name: Helianthus #1
